title: URC Complete Control Program (CCP)
description:
URC's Complete Control Program is a software suite for programming the entire range of URC Professional Remotes that fall under the Complete Control line of products.

Complete Control Program has the ability to control the following remote models:

- MX-780
- MX-880
- MX-880z
- MX-890
- MX-900
- MX-980
- MX-1200
- MX-5000
- MX-6000

- KP-900
- KP-4000

- MRX-1
- MRF-260
- MRZ-260
- MRF-350
- MSC-400

Compatible with Windows XP, Vista, Windows 7 & Windows 8

Version: CCPSetup 03-26-2013

Filename: CCPSetup_2013_03_26.rar
